            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Why Budget-Friendly Doesn't Mean Less Romantic</h2>
            
            <div class="feature-grid">
              <div class="feature-item">
                <h3>üíù Thoughtfulness Over Price</h3>
                <p>Choosing a great affordable spot shows you value experiences over expensive gestures. It's about the thought, not the cost.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="feature-item">
                <h3>üòå Less Pressure</h3>
                <p>When you're not worried about the bill, you can relax and enjoy each other's company. That's what date night is really about.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="feature-item">
                <h3>üéØ Quality Over Luxury</h3>
                <p>Many of LA's best chefs run casual spots with incredible food at accessible prices. You're getting the same talent, just in a relaxed setting.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="feature-item">
                <h3>üåü More Dates</h3>
                <p>When dates are affordable, you can go out more often. Regular date nights strengthen relationships more than occasional splurges.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="content-section">
            <h2>15 Amazing Date Night Restaurants Under $50</h2>

            <div class="restaurants-list">
              {budgetRestaurants.map((restaurant, index) => (
                <div class="restaurant-feature">
                  <div class="restaurant-number">{index + 1}</div>
                  <div class="restaurant-info">
                    <h3>
                      <a href={`/losangeles/${restaurant.slug}/`}>{restaurant.name}</a>
                    </h3>
                    <div class="restaurant-details">
                      <span class="cuisine">{restaurant.cuisineTypes.join(', ').replace(/_/g, ' ')}</span>
